summary: An email from an FBI Special Agent in New York to an unspecified recipient, requesting a conversation regarding a call with the SDNY (Southern District of New York) about a request on the Epstein case. It indicates ongoing investigative coordination.

persons.name: SSA FBI New York
persons.context: The sender of the email, an FBI Special Agent in New York, is requesting a call to discuss a request from the SDNY regarding the Epstein case.

events.title: SDNY call regarding Epstein case request
events.description: The FBI Special Agent has a scheduled call with the Southern District of New York (SDNY) to discuss a request related to the Epstein case.

keyFacts: An FBI Special Agent in New York was coordinating with the SDNY on the Epstein case as of May 2019.
The email indicates an active investigative request from the SDNY to the FBI regarding the Epstein case.
The communication shows inter-agency coordination between the FBI and the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York.
